item.description:
@MentiosRSPS wrote:

[quote=“Loveandpower, post:2, topic:530177”]How many years of experience are you actually looking for? I do have prior forum software experience (vb/smf), never worked with IPB but I’m sure it isn’t that much different. From what I hear it’s quite ajax heavy.

I’m no Ruby but I do know enough for the basic rsps. You didn’t state what exactly you are looking for. Just stating sql experience, website skills doesn’t say a lot.

Edit: and I’d love to have the opportunity to learn more about IPB as I don’t fool around with cracked software so never had the chance. :P[/quote]

No matter how much you’re experienced, you need only know about creating websites and updating them. Also I need administrator for forums to keep it tuned. You don’t have to be super-experienced genius.
